{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act46side", "eventName": "雪山降臨1101", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OS-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "綠翡翠", "storyInfo": "蔓珠院以謝拉格近期的外交問題為由問罪於恩希歐迪斯。維多利亞人強行檢查礦場，發現其中藏有大量仿造重型武器失敗所剩的廢鐵。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g10_manorhouse", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾天，想和你見一面，還真是不容易。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……恩希歐迪斯。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "未能出席大夫人的葬禮，實在抱歉。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲夫人，我為布朗陶家的遭遇深感遺憾，如果有任何希瓦艾什家能幫上忙的地方，請務必相告。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，恩希歐迪斯。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過今天我來找你，也不是為了說這些的。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲夫人此次來訪，想必是要給我一個贏得信任的機會。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼……姐姐說過，你放低姿態的時候，就是最難以令人信任的時候。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不知休露絲夫人又是如何看待我的呢？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用這樣拐彎抹角的，我不喜歡。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……以前姐姐一直責駡我衝動，說話辦事不經過腦子……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想向她證明，證明我不需要躲藏在她的羽翼下，證明我能夠為布朗陶家做點什麼。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如今，我是布朗陶的家主，已經沒有人能來評判我的“證明”了。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以理解，我也有……兩個妹妹。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你看來，聖女大人，與恩希亞……她們都比我還聰明許多吧？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲夫人自謙了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我倒是認為，她們也有與你相似的執著與決心。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希亞她還好嗎？我聽說，她也遇到了意外。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝休露絲夫人記掛，她並無大礙，已經回家了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯先生永遠是這樣一副處變不驚的樣子……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想問，對這些發生在謝拉格的襲擊，包括我姐姐的事……你早有預料嗎？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來這才是休露絲夫人今天來訪的目的……", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯，姐姐她一直在幫你做事，是不是？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對此並非一無所知，但是直到姐姐發生意外後我才發現……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們的計劃，關於維多利亞、萊茵生命以及莫希在追查的事……還有太多我不知道的事。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要否認，不要騙我，恩希歐迪斯，你一定知道關於她遇害的真相。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲夫人，如果你認為大夫人的死與我——", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……你誤會我的意思了。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我不知道菈塔托絲究竟在和你謀劃什麼，但我相信，她一定是在做保護謝拉格的事。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼……我也會做與她一樣的事……布朗陶家的事，不論什麼，我都會承擔。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我需要你告訴我，姐姐她到底——", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，恩希歐迪斯老爺，他們無論如何都要闖進來——", "name": "希瓦艾什家護衛"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位就這樣闖入我家中，到底有何貴幹？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#7$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯大人，喀蘭貿易為何私自將謝拉格與卡西米爾聯合礦場的股份盡數轉讓給維多利亞？", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這是哪裡來的消息？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今礦場已經全面由維多利亞人接管，這已經是人人可見的事實了。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿德頌大長老認為，喀蘭貿易這樣的舉動已有私通他國之嫌，蔓珠院不得不行使權力介入了。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們要求你現在就去蔓珠院，為此事說明。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽蔓珠院的意思，這是要正式審問希瓦艾什家了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今謝拉格人心惶惶，我們也不願意看到矛盾愈演愈烈。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是恩希歐迪斯大人為一族之長，如果還自認為對謝拉格負有責任，請現在就前往蔓珠院，與我們共商對策。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我當然不會推辭。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但既然要說明情況，整理好相關文件還需要一點時間，請容我做好準備。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，我與休露絲夫人還有一些話沒說完，請修士暫且等候。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，恩希歐迪斯大人。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……休露絲夫人，感謝你最近能抽出時間關照恩希亞，我想正式邀請你來希瓦艾什家做客。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也想與她一起當面感謝你的關心。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什……？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按禮數，我本來該正式送上邀請函。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事出倉促，我臨時手寫一張，請休露絲夫人見諒。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屆時恭候休露絲夫人光臨。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不等對方回應，他徑直從桌上拿起紙筆，幾筆寫完後遞了過去。"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲接過。這不是“邀請函”，紙上只有一串地址。"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……感謝你的邀請。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會按時到的。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g11_karlanheadquarters", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "致喀蘭貿易諾希斯先生", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n敬啟者。", "x": 380.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n在您看到這封信時，我還未被授予萊茵生命情況通報權限，所以請您注意——", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n這封信並不是在履行萊茵生命與喀蘭貿易的任何協議與條約，僅代表我個人對謝拉格近期現象的分析。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n我的樣本源於1101年12月7日凌晨3點19分，觀測站收集到的聲波。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "能夠確定的是，在這個時間，有一不明物體從空中墜落到喀蘭聖山上。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n雖然該現象目前的關聯性證據還不夠完整，但三十二小時後，天災確鑿地發生了。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n我並不是有意將兩件事情放在一起思考，如果本次墜落是歷史上唯一一次，那麼天災也是同樣的性質。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "而目前我準備做的，就是確認二者間是否存在實質上的關聯。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n同時，也請恕我冒昧地向您坦誠相告，這種關聯所推導出的假設，對謝拉格如今的情況來說並不樂觀——", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n千百年間，保護謝拉格免受天災的某種因素，現在或許已經失效，或者，其狀態已經不再穩定。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "當然，我很願意證實這只是假設而已。不過我也希望喀蘭貿易對此可能帶來的風險給予足夠的關注。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n掌握更詳盡資料的內部人士——卡羅琳，很有可能已經做出了類似的推斷，但她的目的我也暫時無從知曉。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n我會堅持客觀和理性態度完成這個研究，如果喀蘭貿易支持我的行為，本人將不勝感激。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n\\n\\n埃琳娜，敬上。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "進來吧。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1162_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總監，我正要找您。", "name": "喀蘭貿易員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把這封信交給恩希歐迪斯，機密等級最高。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1162_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，我現在就去處理。", "name": "喀蘭貿易員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有什麼事情嗎？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1162_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，之前派去礦區的觀察哨發來了目擊報告。", "name": "喀蘭貿易員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一批有著維多利亞標誌的車隊正在接近礦區外圍，但不知道確切的來歷。", "name": "喀蘭貿易員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "角峰先生已經帶領家族人士先行前往，他說會儘量拖延時間，等您的判斷。", "name": "喀蘭貿易員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞人該來還是會來，看來我們也沒必要等待了。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘快準備車輛，角峰不一定能拖住他們很久。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴他，先把主動權交給對方，重點在於觀察，我隨後就到。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G14_miningarea", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……提醒你，在這裡妨礙我的工作不是一個好主意。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也是奉命辦事，前方是機密倉庫，沒有喀蘭貿易的授權，任何人都不能入內。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道沒有人告訴你，開斯特家族已經收購了卡西米爾在這片礦區的全部股權？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#6$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但據我所知，目前尚在交接流程中，我們昨天才接到卡西米爾方面的通知。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我們更需要提前檢查全部資產。你們有任何意見，都等我上報給公爵閣下後由她定奪。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在你需要服從命令，馬上打開倉庫的大門。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#6$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終於有說得上話的人了。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喀蘭貿易的諾希斯·埃德懷斯先生。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來我準備的自我介紹也派不上用場了，先生。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，你也明白，我是代表誰而來的。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由於你們經營不善，造成巨額虧損，公爵閣下決定開除在這片礦區工作的，包括原執行經理在內的主要喀蘭貿易員工。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不否認，業務交接工作也會儘量配合。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好，那就請諾希斯先生打開這個倉庫的大門。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……唯有這點恕難從命。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "角峰所言非虛，機密倉庫確實有相關條例規定，請你和公爵閣下體諒。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以我所拿到的資料來看，這個倉庫是近期臨時提高機密等級的。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對此，諾希斯先生是不是也準備了一套說辭？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能夠解釋。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這間倉庫主要用於存放各種工業廢棄物，但近期淨化系統與負壓通風系統先後產生了故障。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在專業人員處理之前，我們臨時提高了機密等級，嚴格限制出入。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我理解公爵閣下關心她所收購的資產，但為了先生的安全考慮，可否將本次檢查稍作推遲呢？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能為此負責，先將門打開。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，這裡是謝拉格的礦區。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果汙染物外泄或者發生其他危險狀況，謝拉格不排除使用行政手段介入。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生提出自己可以負責前，建議還是再與公爵閣下聯絡——", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是……", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#4$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又見面了，角峰先生。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，修士，可能要麻煩你在接待室暫歇，維多利亞大使正與我商議交接工作。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾希斯先生，我正是維多利亞人邀請而來的。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……蔓珠院何時對世俗事務如此關心了？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今，無論家族高層還是民眾，都對喀蘭貿易與維多利亞接觸的方式感到不滿。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大長老已經傳喚恩希歐迪斯大人問詢相關事務，或許不久後，你也需要去一趟蔓珠院。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼在此之前，修士為什麼會應邀來到這裡呢？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要確保交接工作的順利，也希望喀蘭貿易能夠儘量合作。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請打開倉庫大門，諾希斯先生。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三族還政後，恐怕蔓珠院，才更能代表謝拉格的“行政手段”吧？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "角峰，打開大門。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_dooropen", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大門緩緩打開，漫天飛揚的灰塵超乎維多利亞大使的預料，他擠著眼睛，朝面前揮手，搧了搧風。"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有工業廢棄物的味道，也沒有源石煙塵的質感。大使的雙眼逐漸適應，那一覽無遺的廣大倉庫，存放著——"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……全是廢鐵？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#5$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我已經申明，除了工業廢棄物以外，什麼都沒有了。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煩請各位檢查完畢後，儘快離開，久居此處不利於健康。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都留步，我一個人去檢查。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#6$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "false", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_warehouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走入倉庫內，他感到巨大的空間向四面八方延伸，直衝天花板的鋼架上擺滿了形狀不一的各種廢棄金屬。"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "絕不可能為了放置這些東西安排一個大型倉庫，未免過於做作了。"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他走近其中一個貨架的低處，沒有目的地伸手翻找著，金屬碰撞聲在倉庫裡迴響。"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（壓低聲音）等等，這是……", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#5$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（壓低聲音）剩了一半，能看出希瓦艾什的私兵“山雪鬼”的標示。原本是武器裝備，進了粉碎機後沒有處理乾淨嗎……", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#7$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#7$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他想到了什麼，不斷在其他地方翻找著。儘管喀蘭貿易的處理已經十分仔細，但仍有些細碎的線索浮出水面，他暗自肯定著這一點。"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（壓低聲音）仿製維多利亞的新式裝備和大口徑艦炮零件……", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（壓低聲音）全部失敗了，沒有突破技術壁壘……", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍隊番號、徽章，還有許多謝拉格語，他不動聲色地一一記下。"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生！差不多了吧？", "name": "諾希斯"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……啊，好。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#5$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "false", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G14_miningarea", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大使走回眾人身邊。"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實差不多能確定了，感謝諾希斯先生。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會彙總全部情況，如實稟報公爵閣下。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，礦區內部的鐵道剛剛清理完畢，您還沒來得及檢查。", "name": "維多利亞護衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞方面也需要使用那條內部鐵道？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正是，我們已經聯絡了一些供應商進行評估，使用內部鐵道能顯著節約運輸成本。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#5$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修士，蔓珠院對此知情嗎？既然你們希望介入外交事務，喀蘭貿易也希望由你們審核新參與的合作對象。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾希斯關切的詢問打斷了來自蔓珠院的使者的思考，他移開注視著鐵道的目光。"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……還是要等待大長老的指示。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……耶拉岡德在上，請蔓珠院的諸位不要為難恩希歐迪斯，我會在喀蘭貿易總部等候蔓珠院的傳喚。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德在上。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}